window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Rapunzel learned her prophecy by heart years ago, and now, she plays with fate over the details.</p> <p>When she meets a handsome Lord at Grimm Academy, she goes one step further and starts a chain of events which will lead to a bigger betrayal than she ever saw coming.</p> <p>Welcome to Grimm Academy, where fairy tale characters go to avoid their fate.</p> <p><i>Tower of Thorns</i> is an academy retelling of <i>Rapunzel</i> and part of the Once upon an Academy series, set at Grimm Academy.</p>"; 
